reviewText: I love this Dvd when I listen to it something supernatural comes and is the presence of God. In his presence there is joy, peace, healing, miracles, deliverance, breakthrough. If you want to experience any of the above buy this Dvd. One more thing this is in spanish. If you are an american and want to learn spanish go ahead
This dvd is like a workship service! It has some songs that the CD doesn't have with some special guests. I enjoyed it.
Adorei a compra. Esse Dvd  maravilhoso e tambm aprovei a compra nessa empresa, me entregaram 27 dias antes do prazo final. O produto veio novinho e lacrado.

one of the best worship dvds i have ever seen and i don't even speak spanish, it has english subtitles so you can understand the words of the spanish songs, this guy is the best and the band is great also, great quality dvd
